      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that\u2019s been treated with lots of love? This car is in wonderful shape and still drives like a total dream. It's been my trusty companion for a while now, but it's ready for a new home! It\u2019s super clean, looks great inside and out, and is all set for your next big road trip. I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
