    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the individual throttle bodies providing razor-sharp throttle response. The double VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery throughout the rev range. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution. Critically, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis' known fatigue points. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with updated bushings and refreshed dampers, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation. This is a driver-focused example that prioritizes mechanical integrity and longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
