      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2016 Porsche Cayman in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality for the discerning enthusiast. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor road peppering on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the black leather interior remains supple and clean; the cockpit is free of any odors, and all electronics, including the infotainment and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this Cayman is exceptional. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a comprehensive file of maintenance records included. The mid-mounted engine pulls strongly through the gears, and the handling remains as sharp as the day it left the showroom. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and suspension are in excellent working order. This is a turn-key sports car ready for its next owner to enjoy the open road.",
